
Overview of noun hajj

The noun hajj has 1 sense (no senses from tagged texts)
                                          
1. hajj, haj, hadj -- (the fifth pillar of Islam is a pilgrimage to Mecca during the month of Dhu al-Hijja; at least once in a lifetime a Muslim is expected to make a religious journey to Mecca and the Kaaba; "for a Muslim the hajj is the ultimate act of worship")
